  ('heelevel3-722caeab-moex-00024', 'heelevel3-722caeab', 'heelevel3-722caeab-moex-113-10114ebc', 'sub-heelevel3-722caeab-03', NULL, 'essay', '善因行銷（Cause-related Marketing）是將議題、品牌、利他心理而結合
